<doc id="724718" wikidata="Q7720713" url="?curid=724718" title="The Bush Beast">
<text>The Bush Beast was a wooden roller coaster located at Wonderland Sydney in Australia. The ride opened with the park on 7 December 1985 and closed with the park on 26 April 2004. The ride features a mirrored layout to that of other wooden roller coasters located at California&#x27;s Great America, Canada&#x27;s Wonderland, and Kings Dominion. &quot;The Bush Beast&quot; was manufactured by Taft Broadcasting.

